Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所  今天开义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…猪尾吕义…先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副样子除了我以外还会是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是本大爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一直把手压在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在路中间睡午觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是困的话  还是乖乖回家盖被子睡比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是在睡午觉
