Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生  你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能怎么了  你这家伙看到我这副样子什么想法都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生  你看上去满身是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长点眼识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫天乌云呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿个很抢手的东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的  才没有那种东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在托儿所里一直装布娃娃早腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那只熊那里  大吃特吃年轮蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在这种奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长糕一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方糕麻烦来四个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短糕还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我来半份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方糕三人份  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等  现在正在给您做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方糕六人份做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长糕怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等  还有两分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门庭若市啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是瑞祥的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是肯下工夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再多一点花样吧  比如巧克力之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点子不错  试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真熟练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始还想会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在似乎干出感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能用讽刺来形容了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  还开始了送货上门服务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊的年轮蛋糕店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？不是平常的小鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你是打工的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也做过一阵子打工小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被任性的雇主耍得团团转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要说的只有这些吗  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还去过像迷宫一样的房子  那里真是个不可思议的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有好多奇怪的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到现在的你们如此融入自己的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都完全忘记你们以前是什么样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副身体也不坏哦  就是毛太多了有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要注意一点倒也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯还真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至觉得自己从出生起就一直是这副模样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:06:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  竟发生过那种事  感觉就像是一场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我们来说是场恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉已经过去很久了呢  自那以来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来想想  我们没有胜算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找错对手了  简直就是单方面被蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一溃败起来还真是快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉那时好像踩到谁了  是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玄琥大人吗  对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说也没空为那种事一一生气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那时的我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也别说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再怎么不承认  规矩就是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有一边烤年轮蛋糕  一边等这件事的余热消散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在应该反省啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真可惜」这种不要命的话就算心里想也不能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再敢和天界作对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次我们就不只是变成熊和鸟就能解决问题了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会变成泰迪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这家伙别说变成鸟了  顶多变成鸟食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不要那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把自己变得可爱的样子真是太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  今后绝对不要再惹乱子了啊  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许吃  那是我店里重要的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果只肯送给我一盒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小气的熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃了甜食之后就想吃点咸的食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吃了咸的食物以后再吃掉这蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有呢  咸的食物  没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是酱油味好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的心情…  咸味比较配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…那种能刺激一下胃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  解围失误
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  球回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小鬼们  一个个都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个破球有什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是你们的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不行  这是本大爷的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轮蛋糕对你们来说太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不适可而止的话  我就把你们烤了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…你们这帮混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…死也不会…把这个盒子…交给你们…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐不出火就要吐血了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体好重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祸不单行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个的话  一下子就能干了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干燥机比想象中的还要猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那里的蔬菜店…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不  这个要等回去以后慢慢品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是跑腿回去时忍不住的小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个很好闻的味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  那个奇怪的生命体是…
Comment: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:14.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到摩可拿乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边小小的女士们  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别因为开心过头而迷路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家尽情地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误入奇怪的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  每一样看上去都很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我虽然是布娃娃但又不是布娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然年轮蛋糕的盒子就要被别人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么爸爸都能帮你弄到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我想要那个蓝色的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打偏了啊  哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中弹道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又打偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  它是不是动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有动啦  是爸爸太臭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  越是打不中爸爸就越热血沸腾起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一定要打中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下一发会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  都这么大个人了就别较真了  快放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙X4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总也打不中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给老身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老身过去可是被人畏惧地称作「神枪小香菜」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  不倒下是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那大家齐心协力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不带这么玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个蓝色的不倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要被当成小鬼的礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了呢  找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  刚才掉下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  肯定的  大家都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…  倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这里就能暂时安心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你因为海报被人揭下来  所以才东奔西跑到这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁都不来义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪  毕竟那么小的规模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算海报没被揭  区区托儿所的义卖会也没办法抱太大期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此  我当初如果不提出办义卖会会不会比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是决定了的事就要做到底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使遇到困难也不可以放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使浑身湿透再加上被狙击手狙击也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  去做是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有客人也不必那么沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你回来啦  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看  卖了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴天娃娃也卖出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小鸠  我买到了意想不到的好东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要傻站着到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了这么多客人  人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快点来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小鸠你的努力才招来了这么多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起来都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是小鸠你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能专程前来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  说实话  我本想买小鸠亲手给我的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我也有摆摊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没卖出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不知是鸡还是企鹅还是山羊的谜之生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有个性的品位呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…  小兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂…堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是美妙的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  老子说的话你没听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  算了  最重要的「那个」保护到了最后  这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回去了我要立即吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要好好品尝「那个」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「那个」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」是哪个啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子的年轮蛋糕没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  回托儿所拿回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  年轮蛋糕的话很快就卖掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞…搞…搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生说要去拿个很抢手的东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很抢手的东西」就是指年轮蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的分数是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在你对义卖会的热情给80分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上让老子失望的分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总计-300分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失望是因为我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的话我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是道歉能解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我送你我做的可爱的小兔子  别生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我再多送你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再加上这个可爱的小熊和小羊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  哪个是哪个都分不清  全都是谜之生命体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  太过分了  猪尾吕义先生
